step_data.thought: The current page is the address book page, and there are options to change the billing and shipping addresses. The user needs to change the billing address to be different from the shipping address. The 'Change Billing Address' and 'Change Shipping Address' links are available on this page. I will click on the 'Change Billing Address' link to proceed with updating the billing address.
